Small test repository to figure out how to do that cool scrolling
thing I see in articles like
http://www.chcf.org/publications/2013/05/humboldt-story#mixedmedia=F75060C2-FA5D-4F1B-B004-7F37AF6A33A1

The effect is really cool - and technically not hard - even though it
looked mysterious to me when I first saw it. There is a great tutorial
that I used to create this example. See
http://tympanus.net/codrops/2013/05/02/fixed-background-scrolling-layout/
for more information - and more professional images.
